Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.33,0:00:02.67,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amagiri Shinmei Style
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Um...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.14,0:00:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A-Amagiri Shinmei Style First Sword,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Twin Dragons!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.65,0:00:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's call it a day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you very much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Sis Haru sure is powerful, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saya-chan?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:00:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were watching?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, listen...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About that favor...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- Can't we just forget about—\N- Nope.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But see, yelling out the name\Nof the move is kind of embarrassing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.90,0:01:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, it's not.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's totally cool, so don't worry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You think so?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You'll be fine.\NYou'll get used to it soon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay, then, about the favor\NI'm gonna ask you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:29.54,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FAVOR TICKET
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.21,0:01:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to beat my sister once,\Nno matter what.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you think you can help me out?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amaryllis!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.56,0:01:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're in training now,\Nso what's with the daydreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:35.34,ArcName,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking the Memory Barrier
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Eclipse Festa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruka Amagiri lost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, I hear that she didn't actually die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Julis...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought,\Nyour mind is on your sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You said before that you wouldn't go\Nout of your way to search for your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you're afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why your sister sealed your powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why she vanished without a word...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you're reunited with her,\Nthe reason will become clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But precisely because you love her,\Nthe fear must be real, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The fear that your sister might\Nactually have abandoned you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that just might be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's painful to be rejected\Nby someone you cherish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know that all too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's also a fact that you can\Nnever move on at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need to think long and hard\Nabout searching for your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Afraid, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Help me get down from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops-a-daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya, I told you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to scare me so much, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't get through to you\Non your cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what was it\Nyou wanted to see me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I should be asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is it that's bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you heard about it from Julis?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Riessfeld's really worried\Nabout you, Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:06:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, she'd never turn to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato, do you really believe\Nthat Big Sis Haru abandoned you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I assure you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's absolutely no way\NBig Sis Haru would ever abandon you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, if Big Sis Haru\Nreally did lose to someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,not that I can believe it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but if that really is the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then it might be that she just has\Nno way of contacting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, you can't afford\Nto sit around here, brooding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're absolutely right, Saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that sounds more like my Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:07:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato, do you remember this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Favor Ticket, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a blast from the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You and I were always competing\Nwith those tickets on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Using this ticket to call in a favor,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you and I took on Big Sis Haru together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, of course I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like your swordsmanship's\Na lot better now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All that basic training paid off, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that's all... you ever...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}let me do...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:07:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saya-chan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leave it to me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now this is actually...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ayato!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think I panicked just a little.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess it would be insulting\Nif I didn't go all-out in return, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first of the Amagiri Shinmei Style\NHidden Techniques...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Banish Evil Spirits.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Banish Evil Spirits...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we never did manage\Nto beat Big Sis Haru even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my sister was totally unstoppable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she was always\Nso laid-back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's also true of you, Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to find Big Sis Haru\Nand get the best of her next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You and me both, Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'm pretty sure\Nwe still can't beat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when that day comes,\Nall we have to do is join forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So Ayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you're in trouble,\Nyou should lean on someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there are other people\Nwho'd help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though I kind of hate to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see from their\Nprevious matches,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,these twins focus on attacking\Nonly their opponents' weak points.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They create a situation where they have\Nan insurmountable advantage,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and only then do they\Ngo on the offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They sound like trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That said, for this match only,\Nthere is one thing in our favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In our favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it's true that these twins only\Nattack their opponents' flaws,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:11:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then this time around,\Nthat flaw couldn't be more obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My seal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, we should be able to gauge\Nwhat kind of tactics they'll go for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Buying time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So with that in mind,\Nhow should we counter them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only strategy\NI could come up with, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At last, the final match\Nof the quarterfinals is upon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:31.44,Sign Left Mid,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SAYA SASAMIYA\NKIRIN TOUDOU
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:31.44,Sign Right NB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOROTEO LEMUS\NELLIOT FORSTER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:31.44,Sign Left NB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ERNESTA KUHNE\NCAMILLA PARETO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And since all the other matches played\Nat other venues have concluded,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}three of the berths for the semifinals\Nhave been locked up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which team will claim\Nthat last semifinal spot?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First, here's the duo\Nfrom Seidoukan,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ayato Amagiri\Nand Julis-Alexia von Riessfeld!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And their opponents... the team\Nfrom Jie Long Seventh Institute,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shenyun Li and Shenhua Li!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the match to watch!\NBoth teams have taken the field!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:12:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such an epic weak point unmasked,\Nyet you didn't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Either you've got nerves of steel,\Nor you're just stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or else, do you actually\Nhave some kind of strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Only thing is,\Nwe don't plan to lose to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you've got up your\Nsleeve, but I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though we're going to win\Nin the end anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need to do\Nis what we should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the sword inside me,\NI shall break out of this starry prison{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and release my savage force!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There it is, there it is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amagiri's performance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, wait, it's not a performance, is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The majority view seems to be{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that it's a necessary step\Nfor releasing his sealed powers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see, I see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:13:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, wait, wouldn't you know,\Nit's time for the match to begin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Phoenix Festa, Match #4\Nof the quarterfinals...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Battle start!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're fast.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But not so fast that I can't dodge it\Nif I can see it coming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom, Primrose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Make it happen at once, Edict!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:24.18,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EDICT
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoa! Already a smoke screen\Nthis early in the match!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are they planning to fight\Nhidden by the smoke?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew they'd go for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This smoke... it's probably fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see, a mirage, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we can't see a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Show us the match!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:13:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,audiences these days\Nare so impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that was enough\Nfor our purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, one minute has passed\Nsince the match began!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For Amagiri, who can only manifest\Nhis powers up to five minutes,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}this one minute is significant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about twisted personalities!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, those two are pretty impatient, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then, shall I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, it looks\Nlike we're ready to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.05,0:14:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but waiting for you to make a move\Nwould be a bit dull, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and it would probably\Nbore the audience, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get everyone pumped up,\Nor we might get booed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:15:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we make a big splash here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato, watch your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there's only one\Nwho's real among them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that was an illusion?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad! Wrong one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That just won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But the thing is, we're out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cover you,\Nso you take out Shenyun first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Livingstone Daisy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So they're coming after me, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since you can't see\Nthe talismans Shenhua released.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Released?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While that smoke screen was up, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, all we have to do\Nis burn them all away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in this battle, too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Summoning Thunder!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me!\NYou take out Shenyun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be the same\Nif I slash all five of them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.41,0:17:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad. You guessed wrong again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two more to go...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which is the real one?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amagiri Shinmei Style First Sword...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Twin Dragons!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Another one?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, have you reached your limit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the reason for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but it's certainly inconvenient, that seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So how are you feeling right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that... this match\Nhasn't been decided yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can you believe it?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The seemingly drained Amagiri\Nhas pulled off a comeback victory!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So he pretended he'd fallen\Nfor their stalling tactics,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then lured them\Ninto letting down their guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that was close, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just like they say,\N"He who understands destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:19:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,does not stand under a wall\Non the verge of collapse," eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was I really only\Ntaking on the clones the whole time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}after the smoke screen?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think I merely used those clones\Nto get within striking distance of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'd never do\Nsuch an idiotic thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, in your current state,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,even these won't be easy\Nfor you to evade, will they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, how will you dodge them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let myself lose\Nin a place like this yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So even you get that look\Non your face sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that really stirs me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I like that struggling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.37,0:20:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I find it so thrilling!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, it is a shame,\Nbut I think I'm going to end this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stretch out your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks, Julis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had some trouble\Ngetting away from Shenhua.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We each have a wish, and we're both\Nout to do what we can for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:21:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The trouble with you is, you're always\Ntrying to take everything on alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What you said to me once...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me fire back\Nthose exact same words.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,who's going to protect you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done chatting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about we resume this battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, they have\Nsome invisible talismans ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to do something\Nabout that, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.13,0:21:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No... thanks to you, I've awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This time for sure, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So now I have a favor\Nto ask of my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.44,0:23:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At last... at last,\Nthe time has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.95,0:23:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looking back, it was a long\Nand grueling road.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.45,0:23:35.50,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But from now on,\Nit will be my time, all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:40.00,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 16\NNever Back Down
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.50,0:23:38.67,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The whole universe revolves\Naround Ayato and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.67,0:23:40.00,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss it!
